\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3.18}{\ignorespaces Experimental observation of three unidentified molecular lines in $^{87}$Sr. (Top) Data 195 showing a resonance at $259.01 \pm 0.12$ MHz ($I = 19$ W/cm$^2$). (Middle) Data 171 showing a resonance at $274.83 \pm 0.03$ MHz ($I = 5.2$ W/cm$^2$). (Bottom) Data 184 showing a resonance at $375.74 \pm 0.48$ MHz ($I = 5.2$ W/cm$^2$). All detunings are measured from the $^{87}$Sr atomic resonance.}}{56}{figure.caption.173}%
